Help Type: command
Command: spinedigest import

Purpose:
  Import source material into an LLM Wiki archive at source stage.

Usage:
  spinedigest import <archive.sdpub> [source] [--input-format <format>] [--llm <json>] [--prompt <text>]

Contract:
  - Mutates: yes, writes the archive path.
  - LLM: no; import stops at source stage.
  - stdin: supported with --input-format markdown or txt.
  - JSON: no.

Examples:
  spinedigest import book.sdpub ./book.md --input-format markdown
  cat article.md | spinedigest import article.sdpub --input-format markdown
